{"tid":701622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「為了當癡漢才到東京」　男用硬棒頂女乘客下半身被逮","createTime":"2018-06-14T09:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T10:38:04.000Z","uid":72009,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5648888ab1af427210b2ea1e1757d9b29f6fa50e","tid":701622,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:24:10.000Z","msg":"據《NHK》報導，家住兵庫縣的36歲男子佐伯和彦，4月時於下班尖峰時間，搭乘東京JR埼京線的電車，於車廂內以「棒狀物」碰觸20多歲女乘客的下半身，然後還偷拍裙底風光，當時被發現癡漢行為時，佐伯和彦趁電車到站時，跳下月台逃跑，警視廳從監視器畫面鎖定佐伯和彦，後以強制猥褻罪將他逮捕。被逮後佐伯和彦稱「為了當癡漢才到東京，只有偷拍沒有碰到身體」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180614/640_217f9f31e351159193b0e5664981377c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180614%2F640_217f9f31e351159193b0e5664981377c.jpg&h=2fec6bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4780e251c08d61d659636f5c52ed7c9a0c9d3145","tid":701622,"uid":166109,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"痴漢中既真男人"},{"pid":"ce686f16529ade0a033900ef4e03a29beed10a5f","tid":701622,"uid":44823,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:30:24.000Z","msg":"癡漢中既霸主<br />\n<br />\n咁即係咩呀？<br />\n<br />\n癡漢囉"},{"pid":"0e4df477d455d7a5db9e4e022443fb3912efd4e3","tid":701622,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:34:01.000Z","msg":"如果頂pat到射<br />\n真係勁"},{"pid":"019152df553fb828c41185953ed60d330277b2f7","tid":701622,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:34:27.000Z","msg":"出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 哂樣"},{"pid":"3fccc4fd3ff4ab1d31325ea57142493b33f84f43","tid":701622,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"019152df553fb828c41185953ed60d330277b2f7","tid":701622,"uid":75372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0